{"tid":1134022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"奇異博士同奇異種子鬥快食奇異果","createTime":"2019-05-01T13:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T01:39:11.000Z","uid":118557,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d2989f504f2b177c8aaa747ed485d72054821d","tid":1134022,"uid":118557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"邊個會嬴？"},{"pid":"eda5109f69595d7074d34c195579df34566e7a1d","tid":1134022,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"奇異種子可以進化到奇異花再食自己啲果，<br />\n<br />\nWin Win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b42d7084a0ba2548f4aa9aa6bef597439cf57c1","tid":1134022,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"唱埋奇異恩典"},{"pid":"a5b0644e0ab5e048e4f3d262faecd707bf989fa0","tid":1134022,"uid":3847,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"你地都無得救 咁撚戇尻問題都答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f976418123e047370b3fa3aa16a09f8e621849","tid":1134022,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"不思議だね"},{"pid":"48247ed8debcf9bca61291a659e565370f0dadc4","tid":1134022,"uid":232594,"like":17,"dislike":30,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"數學角度黎講，一個人進食速度係同口部面積大小成正比，即係個口愈大能夠同時食落肚既野就愈多，咁我地首先睇下兩位個口既大細<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://is2-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Video82/v4/86/bd/4d/86bd4d75-6991-fbc3-e0df-1b5691f0b804/Checkmate_Global_EST_and_VOD_InHome_Materials_iTunes_LSR_Taiwanese_Taiwan_2000_x_3000.lsr/268x0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis2-ssl.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FVideo82%2Fv4%2F86%2Fbd%2F4d%2F86bd4d75-6991-fbc3-e0df-1b5691f0b804%2FCheckmate_Global_EST_and_VOD_InHome_Materials_iTunes_LSR_Taiwanese_Taiwan_2000_x_3000.lsr%2F268x0w.jpg&h=2ab217d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依上圖目測，奇異博士個口半徑大約4cm，計算得出擘大之後(假設圓型)面積為：<br />\npi * (4^2) ~= 50.27cm^2<br />\n<br />\n再睇睇奇異種子個口<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W42GXN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW42GXN9.jpg&h=3e71fbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目測半徑應該有10cm，計算得出面積為：<br />\npi * (10^2) ~= 314.16cm^2<br />\n<br />\n比較之下， 314.16 &gt; 50.27，由此可見奇異種子於同時間之下能夠食到既奇異果係比奇異博士多~6倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a54ab3c9d4fbeed53a02b0ee26293436deee97","tid":1134022,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:01:48.000Z","msg":"所以贏既會係奇異種子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3deac26927c4f1c5211fbf8aa7e20a6957ff31b0","tid":1134022,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48247ed8debcf9bca61291a659e565370f0dadc4","tid":1134022,"uid":232594,"like":17,"dislike":30,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"數學角度黎講，一個人進食速度係同口部面積大小成正比，即係個口愈大能夠同時食落肚既野就愈多，咁我地首先睇下兩位個口既大細<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://is2-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Video82/v4/86/bd/4d/86bd4d75-6991-fbc3-e0df-1b5691f0b804/Checkmate_Global_EST_and_VOD_InHome_Materials_iTunes_LSR_Taiwanese_Taiwan_2000_x_3000.lsr/268x0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis2-ssl.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FVideo82%2Fv4%2F86%2Fbd%2F4d%2F86bd4d75-6991-fbc3-e0df-1b5691f0b804%2FCheckmate_Global_EST_and_VOD_InHome_Materials_iTunes_LSR_Taiwanese_Taiwan_2000_x_3000.lsr%2F268x0w.jpg&h=2ab217d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依上圖目測，奇異博士個口半徑大約4cm，計算得出擘大之後(假設圓型)面積為：<br />\npi * (4^2) ~= 50.27cm^2<br />\n<br />\n再睇睇奇異種子個口<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W42GXN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW42GXN9.jpg&h=3e71fbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目測